{"segment_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-002", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao", "source_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 皐陶謨 [2]", "text_original": "禹曰：「俞！如何？」", "text_normalized": "禹曰：「俞！如何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-003", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao", "source_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 皐陶謨 [3]", "text_original": "皋陶曰：「都！慎厥身，修思永。惇敘九族，庶明勵翼，邇可遠，在茲。」", "text_normalized": "皋陶曰：「都！慎厥身，修思永。惇敘九族，庶明勵翼，邇可遠，在茲。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-004", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao", "source_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 皐陶謨 [4]", "text_original": "禹拜昌言曰：「俞！」", "text_normalized": "禹拜昌言曰：「俞！」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-005", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao", "source_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 皐陶謨 [5]", "text_original": "皋陶曰：「都！在知人，在安民。」", "text_normalized": "皋陶曰：「都！在知人，在安民。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-006", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao", "source_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 皐陶謨 [6]", "text_original": "禹曰：「吁！咸若時，惟帝其難之。知人則哲，能官人安民則惠。黎民懷之，能哲而惠，何憂乎驩兜？何遷乎有苗？何畏乎巧言令色孔壬？」", "text_normalized": "禹曰：「吁！咸若時，惟帝其難之。知人則哲，能官人安民則惠。黎民懷之，能哲而惠，何憂乎驩兜？何遷乎有苗？何畏乎巧言令色孔壬？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-007", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao", "source_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 皐陶謨 [7]", "text_original": "皋陶曰：「都！亦行有九德，亦言其人有德，乃言曰，載采采。」", "text_normalized": "皋陶曰：「都！亦行有九德，亦言其人有德，乃言曰，載采采。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-008", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao", "source_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 皐陶謨 [8]", "text_original": "禹曰：「何？」", "text_normalized": "禹曰：「何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-009", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao", "source_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 皐陶謨 [9]", "text_original": "皋陶曰：「寬而栗。柔而立，愿而恭，亂而敬，擾而毅，直而溫，簡而廉，剛而塞，彊而義，彰厥有常。吉哉！日宣三德，夙夜浚明有家。日嚴祗敬六德，亮采有邦，翕受敷施。九德咸事，俊乂在官。百僚師師，百工惟時。撫于五辰，庶績其凝。無教逸欲。有邦兢兢業業，一日二日萬幾。無曠庶官，天工人其代之。天敘有典，勑我五典五惇哉！天秩有禮，自我五禮有庸哉！同寅協恭和衷哉！天命有德，五服五章哉！天討有罪，五刑五用哉！政事懋哉懋哉！天聰明，自我民聰明，天明畏自我民明威。達于上下，敬哉有土。」", "text_normalized": "皋陶曰：「寬而栗。柔而立，愿而恭，亂而敬，擾而毅，直而溫，簡而廉，剛而塞，彊而義，彰厥有常。吉哉！日宣三德，夙夜浚明有家。日嚴祗敬六德，亮采有邦，翕受敷施。九德咸事，俊乂在官。百僚師師，百工惟時。撫于五辰，庶績其凝。無教逸欲。有邦兢兢業業，一日二日萬幾。無曠庶官，天工人其代之。天敘有典，勑我五典五惇哉！天秩有禮，自我五禮有庸哉！同寅協恭和衷哉！天命有德，五服五章哉！天討有罪，五刑五用哉！政事懋哉懋哉！天聰明，自我民聰明，天明畏自我民明威。達于上下，敬哉有土。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-010", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao", "source_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 皐陶謨 [10]", "text_original": "皋陶曰：「朕言惠，可厎行。」", "text_normalized": "皋陶曰：「朕言惠，可厎行。」", "notes": ""}
