{"segment_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-012", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao", "source_id": "shangshu-005-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-gao-yao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 皐陶謨 [12]", "text_original": "皋陶曰：「予未有知，思曰贊贊襄哉！」", "text_normalized": "皋陶曰：「予未有知，思曰贊贊襄哉！」", "notes": ""}
